#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.metainfo.xml.in:17
msgid "Dual-panel file manager"
msgstr "ორპანელიანი ფაილების მმართველი"

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.metainfo.xml.in:19
msgid ""
"Gnome Commander is a “dual-panel” graphical file manager. It features separate "
"tabs for each panel, setting up custom device buttons, bookmark manager, fully "
"integrated commandline, file quick search, an internal image viewer, a powerful "
"batch renaming tool, and FTP and Samba access."
msgstr ""

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.metainfo.xml.in:26
msgid ""
"Gnome Commander aims to advanced users who like to focus on precise file "
"management, working in parallel through special applications, and running smart "
"commands."
msgstr ""

